title._content: Illustrated front cover from The Queenslander, December 27, 1928

description._content: Photographer: Agnew, Garnet (Garnet Gerald), 1886-1951 Location:Queensland Description:The New Year's Eve issue depicts a small boy dressed as a swagman with a knapsack on his back and carrying a billy and some items wrapped in a bag. In the distance behind him is a figure of a much older, stooped swagman. The year 1929 is displayed behind the boy.
